{UTF-8}
Average Recovery Time=10
	~	Day
	~		|

Contact Rate=5
	~	Person/Day
	~		|

Healthcare Stress=Infected / Hospital Beds
	~	Dmnl
	~		|

Hospital Beds=150
	~	Bed
	~		|

Infected= INTEG (Infection Rate-Recovery Rate,
		10)
	~	Person
	~		|

Infection Rate=(Susceptible * Infected / Total Population) * Contact Rate * Infectivity
	~	Person/Day
	~		|

Infectivity=0.1
	~	Dmnl
	~		|

Recovered= INTEG (Recovery Rate,
		0)
	~	Person
	~		|

Recovery Rate=Infected / Average Recovery Time
	~	Person/Day
	~		|

Susceptible= INTEG (-Infection Rate,
		990)
	~	Person
	~		|

Total Population=Susceptible + Infected + Recovered
	~	Person
	~		|

********************************************************
	.Control
********************************************************~
